---
title: Sri Lankan-Style Lamb & Veggie Curry with Garlic Rice & Roasted Hazelnuts
description: This dish comes with a big juicy warning - it’s too delicious to refuse. Be lured to the table when you catch the scent of the Sri
Lankan-spiced lamb and veggies, tossed in a tomato-based creamy curry. Look out, that bite of garlic rice, teaming with curry
will unleash the tastiest dinner and you’ll be running back for seconds in no time.
